modules.description: Provides functions to integrate topkg-care with Jbuilder-based projects, including setup and configuration for topkg commands. Works with Jbuilder build configurations and topkg metadata structures. Enables seamless use of topkg for package management without modifying build workflows.

Provides functions to configure package metadata and build settings for jbuilder, including handling readmes, licenses, change logs, and custom linters. Works with package descriptors, file paths, and build configurations. Used to define package details in multi-package projects where OPAM files share a common base name.
